name: NewYorkCityGuide
0:
”Alexa, ask New York City Guide to tell me top five things to do.”
”Alexa, ask New York City Guide to open number one.”
”Alexa, ask New York City Guide to tell me the news”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: new york city guide
des: This app will allow you to explore the wonders and beauty of New York City. Enrich yourself with a guide that can show you the major attractions and sights of the biggest city on the east coast. The New York City app will show you the top 5 things to do in detail. If you still require more information, the app will provide more contact information. Have fun in New York City!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
